(17, 1, 14, 'Nightmare Craft: Mobs Mod (1.18.2) &ndash; The Force comes from the Dark 23', 'Nightmare Craft: Mobs Mod 2', '2022-11-27 16:32:38', '&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;1 223Have you ever wanted to ride a Unicorn? Maybe a Pegasus? Or maybe even&hellip; a Dragon? Or maybe you are more of a fighter and you want to slay epic skeleons, cyclopses, dinosaurs, dragons or even minotaurs? Maybe you just want to watch some butterflies roam around your world along with some deer and some fantastic friendly creatures? Your epic mobs are surely to be found in Nightmare Craft: Mobs Mod (1.18.2). Adventure, thrill and cuteness &ndash; all in one package.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hostile Mobs:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ground Mobs:&lt;/strong&gt;&nbsp;Garbage, Uncommon Skeletons, Pirate Skeletons, Skeleton Cyclops, Pirate Vampires, Agents, Crocodile, Sabertooth, Hogs, Raiders, different spider types, new Endermen, Sandworm, Giant, Minotaur, Dinosaurs&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Flying:&lt;/strong&gt;&nbsp;Dragons&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Underwater:&lt;/strong&gt;&nbsp;Piranhas, Sharks, Killer Squids, Sharks with Lasers on Head, Killer Whales.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Neutral/Passive Mobs:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ground:&lt;/strong&gt;&nbsp;Bears, Deer, Goats, Zebra, Giraffe, Hippo, Centaur, Kitten, Unicorn&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Flying:&lt;/strong&gt;&nbsp;Buttterflies, Seagulls, Fairy, Sprite, Phoenix, Pegasus&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Underwater:&lt;/strong&gt;&nbsp;Whales, Mermaids, Baby Seals, Koi Fish,&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mobs that you can tame:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Goats, Rams, Ostriches, Hippos, Giraffes, Zebras, Unicorns, Pegasus, Gryphon, Dragons.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hunting:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Butterflies can be caught in jars.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Leprechauns can be caught with nets in small crates.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', NULL, b'1'),
