(50, 1, 16, 'Stargate Journey Mod (1.20.1, 1.19.4) – New Interplanetary Portals', 'Stargate Journey Mod', '2023-11-18 19:44:58', '&lt;p&gt;Stargate Journey Mod (1.20.1, 1.19.4) introduces a variety of new structures, blocks, and most importantly, Stargates into Minecraft. Stargates are special portal-like devices that can let a player travel between dimensions. Unlike the vanilla portals, Stargates cannot be built by the player. One had to go in search of special temple-like structures that hold the secrets to finding a Stargate. Let us take a look at some of the important features of this amazing mod.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3&gt;Features:&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Unique Stargate Mechanism:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Stargates cannot be crafted but must be discovered in the world, adding an element of exploration and adventure to the gameplay.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Enables instantaneous travel between different Planets (Dimensions), offering a distinctive way to navigate the Minecraft universe.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Expansive Multiverse:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Beyond the initial Stargate, players can explore multiple worlds with unique characteristics, encouraging further exploration and discovery.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The promise of potentially crafting additional Stargates adds an intriguing long-term goal for players, enhancing the overall gaming experience.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Work-in-Progress Caution:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The mod is explicitly mentioned as a work in progress, with a disclaimer about potential bugs, unfinished features, or elements that might be unattainable in Survival mode.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Players are advised to back up their worlds properly, emphasizing the importance of caution and preparedness when engaging with the mod.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'postimages/2023-11-18-Thumbnail-Stargate-Journey-Mod.png', b'1'),
(51, 1, 16, 'Server Country Flags Mod (1.20.2, 1.19.4) -Server Location Viewer &#38; Map', 'Server Location Viewer & Map Display', '2023-11-18 19:48:06', '&lt;p&gt;If you play on Minecraft servers on a regular basis, Server Country Flags Mod (1.20.2, 1.19.4) is a must have. With this mod installed, the servers in your game&rsquo;s server list will have a tiny flag icon next to the server name to represent the country in which the server is hosted from. There is also a small button with a globe on the lower end of the screen, clicking on which will open up a full screen map that shows the location of the server.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3&gt;Features:&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Enhanced Server Information:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Server Country Flags enriches your Minecraft server list experience by displaying the country in which a server is located, along with your approximate distance to it and additional server details.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;User-Friendly Configuration:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;With the&nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.9minecraft.net/cloth-config-api/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Cloth Config API&lt;/a&gt;, the mod offers a convenient and intuitive graphical user interface for adjusting settings. Forge users can access it through the mod list&rsquo;s Config button, while&nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.9minecraft.net/fabric-loader/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Fabric&lt;/a&gt;&nbsp;users can utilize&nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.mc-mod.net/mod-menu-mod/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Mod Menu&lt;/a&gt;&rsquo;s config button for seamless customization.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;IP Geolocation Integration:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The mod utilizes data from IP-API.com, a publicly available and free IP Geolocation service. While limiting requests to 45 per minute, it ensures sufficient information to identify server locations accurately.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Built-In Server Map:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Server Country Flags comes equipped with a built-in server map, providing a visual overview of server locations. Easily accessible through the server list via the Server Map button, this feature allows users to identify their favorite servers&rsquo; geographical positions at a glance. Customization options for the map&rsquo;s placement and removal are also available in the configuration settings.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'postimages/2023-11-18-2-Server-Country-Flags-Mod.png', b'1'),
(52, 1, 16, 'Erroring Entity Remover Reforged Mod (1.20.1, 1.19.4)', 'Erroring Entity Remover Reforged Mod ', '2023-11-18 19:49:46', '&lt;p&gt;Enter the realm of stability with the Erroring Entity Remover Reforged Mod (1.20.1, 1.19.4), a reliable solution for eliminating problematic entities that can disrupt your Minecraft experience. This mod review explores the key features and benefits of this essential tool for maintaining a smooth and error-free gameplay environment. This mod acts as a guardian against disruptions, allowing players to enjoy Minecraft without the fear of sudden crashes caused by problematic entities. The automatic removal of error-prone entities contributes to a stress-free and reliable gaming experience.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3&gt;Features:&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;The mod actively identifies entities that throw errors during the ticking process, aiming to prevent crashes and maintain a stable gameplay experience.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Addresses a common issue in Minecraft where certain entities can cause errors, leading to unexpected crashes.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Streamlines the error resolution process by automatically removing entities that are prone to causing issues.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Enhances the overall stability of the game by swiftly handling problematic entities without requiring manual intervention.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;This version of the mod represents a reforged and improved iteration, building upon the foundation of the original Erroring Entity Remover.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Incorporates updates and optimizations to ensure compatibility with the latest Minecraft versions and a more robust entity removal system.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Functions seamlessly on both servers and clients, providing a consistent solution for players regardless of their preferred Minecraft environment.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Ensures that multiplayer experiences remain stable by addressing entity-related errors that may impact server performance.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'postimages/2023-11-18-3-il-.png', b'1'),
(53, 1, 16, 'Masik’s Puzzle Dungeon Mod (1.20.1, 1.19.4)', 'Masik’s Puzzle Dungeon Mod', '2023-11-18 19:51:02', '&lt;p&gt;Embark on a thrilling journey with Masik&rsquo;s Puzzle Dungeon Mod (1.20.1, 1.19.4), a mod that introduces a captivating randomly generated structure in the heart of the Jungle biome. This mod spotlight unveils the mysteries and challenges that await players in this intricate puzzle-filled dungeon. Successfully solving puzzles and conquering challenges within the dungeon yields rewarding treasures, making the journey worthwhile for courageous and clever players. Collect unique items, valuable resources, and perhaps even artifacts as you triumph over the dungeon&rsquo;s trials.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3&gt;Features:&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Explore the Jungle biome and stumble upon the fascinating puzzle dungeon, a structure that dynamically generates for a unique experience in each playthrough.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Delve into the unknown as you navigate through a maze of puzzles, traps, and secrets designed to test your wits.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Discover a map leading to Masik&rsquo;s Puzzle Dungeon in shipwreck chests, adding an element of exploration and treasure hunting to your Minecraft adventures.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Follow the clues and embark on a quest to locate the dungeon, unraveling the mysteries hinted at by the map.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Encounter a variety of puzzles that range in complexity, requiring problem-solving skills and creativity to progress through the dungeon.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Overcome challenges, avoid traps, and unlock hidden passages as you navigate through the intricately designed puzzles.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'postimages/2023-11-18-4-Masiks-Puzzle-D.png', b'1'),
(54, 1, 16, 'Skinned Carts Mod (1.20.1, 1.19.4)', 'Skinned Carts Mod', '2023-11-18 19:51:43', '&lt;p&gt;Embark on a delightful and whimsical journey with the Skinned Carts Mod (1.20.1, 1.19.4), where traditional minecarts get a charming makeover in the form of various animal-inspired skins. This mod spotlight highlights the creative and fun additions that Skinned Carts introduces to your Minecraft world. Upgrade your transportation style with a lighthearted and imaginative twist. Combine the functionality of minecarts with the charm of animal skins to create a transportation system that stands out in your Minecraft world.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3&gt;Features:&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Experience a touch of whimsy as minecarts transform into adorable and creative animal-inspired carts.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Discover a variety of skins that bring different animals to life, adding a playful and entertaining element to your transportation system.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Spice up your rail systems by incorporating skinned carts into your transportation networks.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Mix and match different animal skins to create a colorful and personalized railway that reflects your creativity and adds character to your world.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Enjoy the visually appealing aesthetics of animal-shaped minecarts as they roll along the rails.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Whether it&rsquo;s a cart resembling a cute panda, a speedy rabbit, or another animal, each cart adds a unique and enjoyable touch to your Minecraft experience.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'postimages/2023-11-18-5-Masiks-Puzzle-Dungeon-Mod-Thumbnail-.png', b'1'),
(55, 1, 16, 'Weapons Of Miracles Mod (1.20.1, 1.19.2) ', 'Weapons Of Miracles Mod ', '2023-11-18 19:52:22', '&lt;p&gt;Dive into the heart of battle with the Weapons Of Miracles Mod (1.20.1, 1.19.2) addon for the Epic Fight mod by Yesman. This spotlight will showcase the exciting additions and features that this expansion brings to your Minecraft combat experience. Experience an enhanced challenge with dynamic gamerules that make mobs stronger based on their proximity. Encourage strategic battles by rewarding players with emeralds and extra XP for defeating powerful mobs. Enjoy a visually immersive combat experience with unique animations and behaviors for each weapon. Immerse yourself in the dynamic and captivating animations that bring the Weapons of Miracles to life.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3&gt;Features:&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Unleash the power of 10 new weapons, each with its own distinct characteristics and abilities.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Discover the strengths and special techniques of each weapon, adding depth and variety to your combat strategies.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Master 18 new skills that amplify your combat prowess.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Experiment with different combinations of skills to create personalized fighting styles tailored to your playstyle.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Equip yourself with artifacts that go beyond traditional armor, offering unique benefits and enhancing your survivability in battle.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Explore the possibilities of each artifact armor set to find the perfect balance for your adventures.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Unlock the potential of the new enchantment introduced by the Weapons of Miracles expansion.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;Delve into hidden techniques and secrets associated with the weapons, encouraging players to explore and master the full capabilities of each item.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n', 'postimages/2023-11-18-7-Weapons-of-Miracles-Mod-Thumbnail-.png', b'1'),
(56, 1, 16, 'Post Vanilla Data Pack (1.20.2, 1.19.4)', 'Post Vanilla Data Pack', '2023-11-18 19:53:18', '&lt;p&gt;Dive into the whimsical realm of Post Vanilla Data Pack (1.20.2, 1.19.4), a delightful departure from the ordinary. This unique data pack injects a dose of playfulness and eccentricity into your Minecraft adventure, offering an unconventional experience that defies expectations. Enjoy playing this data pack!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3&gt;Features:&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Quirky Mobs:&lt;/strong&gt;&nbsp;Encounter a cast of eccentric creatures that bring a touch of humor to your Minecraft world.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Unusual Biomes:&lt;/strong&gt;&nbsp;Explore unconventional landscapes and biomes that challenge the traditional Minecraft environment.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Wacky Items and Tools:&lt;/strong&gt;&nbsp;Arm yourself with outlandish tools and items, each with its own surprising twist.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Playful Mechanics:&lt;/strong&gt;&nbsp;Experience gameplay mechanics that deviate from the norm, keeping you on your toes.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ripoff Charm:&lt;/strong&gt;&nbsp;Embrace the charm of a Minecraft ripoff that takes itself lightheartedly and introduces unexpected elements.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n', 'postimages/2023-11-18-post-vanilla-thumb.png', b'1');

